node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Vivir Design on July 28, 2021 tagging @beckiowens, @cletile, @splitrockcustomhomes, and @rebekahwestoverphotography. May be an image of kitchen.

node.text:
Happy Wednesday! 
Let’s kick it off with a tour of the kitchen from one of our favorite properties ever!! And that is the #familytiescustom designed by @beckiowens. It still feels as effortlessly cool as the first moment we laid eyes on it. One of our favorite things about it is how many different elements work together here. Black, white, and white oak cabinetry, along with two different colors of countertops. And I wouldn’t change a thing!! Built by the fabulous @splitrockcustomhomes , and shot by the crazy talented @rebekahwestoverphotography 
.
.
.
.
.
.
